query:
SELECT t.task_id, schedule, t.idempotency_key
            FROM task t
            WHERE ($1 = t.task_id or $1 is null) AND t.status = 'enabled' AND (next_tick < now() AT TIME ZONE 'UTC' AND next_tick is not null)
            ORDER BY next_tick
            FOR UPDATE SKIP LOCKED
            LIMIT 1
